      "description": "Peak axial load: 1.5–3.2 kN (corresponding to 2.0–4.0× BW for 80 kg reference patient). Flexion angle range: 0–120°. Tibial insert thickness: 8–14 mm. UHMWPE elastic modulus: 700–1050 MPa. Tibial slope: 0–7°. All five ISO 14243-1 gait load cases must be evaluated; extrapolation beyond these bounds is not supported by this COU."
    }
  },
