      "rationale": "Simulation workflow documented in a controlled simulation execution plan (SEP) with step-by-step procedures for mesh generation, boundary condition application, and post-processing. Two independent analysts executed the workflow on a blinded test case; results agreed within 1.2% for peak contact stress. Peer review of input decks completed by senior engineer not involved in original setup. All deviations from SEP must be documented via NCR process.",
