      "rationale": "Linear elastic model for UHMWPE justified by strain levels < 3% in all production cases (nonlinear effects < 2% per sensitivity study). Augmented Lagrangian contact formulation selected over penalty method to eliminate penetration sensitivity. Tibial tray modeled as rigid (stainless steel modulus 200 GPa vs UHMWPE 900 MPa; rigidity assumption error < 0.3% per parametric study). Model form assumptions documented and justified in the Modeling and Simulation Report.",
